experienceContent.htmlText: HOLEOExperience is a great place to spend time with family and friends. Come on, take them to the HOLEOExperience at Cove at Batavia PIK from 5 August to 10 September 2023.
Here, you can play mini golf with beautiful seaside views. Then, the decoration of the mini golf is also very cute and unique.

list: Cancellations made less than 1 day(s) prior to selected visit date are not eligible for a refund.
